import "../css/Contact.css"; export const Contact = () => { return (

Contact Info

Please email or call me with any questions or to set up a lesson:

info@thelordofthestrings.com

 (213) 479-4508

I am open for in-studio lessons every day of the week, except Friday, from 10AM-9PM, but only until 5PM on Sat and Sun.

Skype lessons can be set up anytime. Please email me to arrange scheduling.

"In Studio" lessons in Los Angeles area are conducted at my home studio, located conveniently near the 10 and 405 freeways, in the West LA/Mar Vista area, east of the Santa Monica Airport. The building is right next door to the Whole Foods at National/Barrington.

11650 National Blvd.

Los Angeles, CA 90064

Please email me for instructions to get into the building.
